hey!

my name's tom and i want to help you and myself be more discerning about the makeup we purchase. I have a history of overspending on makeup and I don't ever want to find myself in that situation again. on my channel I do videos like Critical Sass where I talk about new makeup releases and unpack the makeup marketing. I will try to help talk you out of purchases you may haven't fully thought through OR help you realize the purchase you want to make will actually add value to your makeup collection. I also do a lot of makeup testing to find out of these brands are actually making product that could be worth your time. I always want to approach makeup through the fun that it has always provided me and I hope that's what you'll find on this channel.

my name's tom and i want to help you and myself be more discerning about the makeup we purchase. I have a history of overspending on makeup and I don't ever want to find myself in that situation again. on my channel I do videos like Critical Sass where I talk about new makeup releases and unpack the makeup marketing. I will try to help talk you out of purchases you may haven't fully thought through OR help you realize the purchase you want to make will actually add value to your makeup collection. I also do a lot of makeup testing to find out of these brands are actually making product that could be worth your time. I always want to approach makeup through the fun that it has always provided me and I hope that's what you'll find on this channel.

aboutChannelInfo/channelDescription:
hey!

my name's tom and i want to help you and myself be more discerning about the makeup we purchase. I have a history of overspending on makeup and I don't ever want to find myself in that situation again. on my channel I do videos like Critical Sass where I talk about new makeup releases and unpack the makeup marketing. I will try to help talk you out of purchases you may haven't fully thought through OR help you realize the purchase you want to make will actually add value to your makeup collection. I also do a lot of makeup testing to find out of these brands are actually making product that could be worth your time. I always want to approach makeup through the fun that it has always provided me and I hope that's what you'll find on this channel.

xx
